Xenophobia and intolerance run rampant throughout all levels of this game as well as all levels of society outside the game.<br>
<br>
The simple fact that people get upset by an abbreviation such as plz or pst and feel the need to make multiple posts about it after it has been beaten to death already is pretty much proof of that.<br>
<br>
'Course that's just my opinion. You're welcome to yours.<br>
