I'm laughing at the people who whine about those who whine about the abbreviation PST.<br>
<br>
PST is unnecessary. I laugh at the ignorance of those who use it.<br>
<br>
But I laugh more at the fools who whine at the whiners. If YOU don't see why someone else doesn't like 'PST', well, fair enough, but if you are just whining about them whining, what does that make you?<br>
<br>
It begins with Hypo and ends with crite. And you probably don't get it either.<br>
