Does it? If you you /auction WTS Cloth Cape and they respond in /auction did the sentence mean the same thing? Obviously not or they would have sent you a tell. I see this all the time. Someone /shout 52 Chanter LFG and another person yells /shout 54 Chanter LFG and then I see /shout Chanter to CE. Now which chanter were they referring to??? I've been the wrong chanter before when I was the 52 chanter when I missed that some other chanter gave a LFG. A simple <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> PST</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> solves the problem. Sorry you don't like it. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
