<br>
You can mock it as much as you want but I trade alot and have just found that there are much fewer hassles if I simply add a PST at the end of my /auction. However I would have no problem if you wanted to have a mass campaign to educate people to always respond to questions with a tell. But in my opinion its much easier to simply add a big ole <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> PST</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> to the end of my /auction. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
